data.description: A rare opportunity to have it all! Lovingly maintained and upgraded, nestled at the center of a vibrant community that provides not only a home, but a lifestyle. Upper floor includes an oversized Primary with beautifully updated bath, and an additional two bedrooms connected by a perfect Jack and Jill. Main floor is bright, clean and inviting, featuring high ceilings and hardwoods. FULLY finished basement, featuring two more bedrooms and a full bath, provides endless flexibility; multi-generational living, media room, storage, offices. Almost more impressive is the community youCOll be joining! Active neighborhood with salt-water pool, cabanas, grills, etc... multiple ALTA teams, new playground, pickleball court, community parties and a dog park! Your life. Your way.
